  "text": "Techniques to prevent the aforementioned cyber-physical attacks have been proposed in the literature. In [CITATION_1] , Franklin et al. describe a signal-based detector method, using discrete wavelet transformations. Brumback and Srinath study in [CITATION_2] strategies for handling cyber-physical attacks using statistical detection methods. Mo et al. propose in [CITATION_3] , [CITATION_4] the use of watermark-based detection by adapting traditional failure detection mechanisms (e.g., detectors to handle faults and errors). In the following sections, we elaborate further on the watermark-based technique by Mo et al., discuss about some security limitations and propose an improved technique.",
